            <p>Guests in Jonker-area Airbnbs don't need a car as major attractions are walkable. Guests in Klebang or Jasin will definitely need a car or ride-sharing apps (Grab) to get around.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2>Conclusion</h2>

<p><strong>Buy Jonker</strong> if you want volume and don't mind the hustle.
<br><strong>Buy Klebang</strong> if you want higher-quality guests and a potential retirement home later.</p>

